<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
    <title>About</title>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <%- include('partials/navbar', {page: '/about'}) %>
    </nav>
        <div class="container mx-auto p-4">
            <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <div class="hero-content text-center ">
                <div class="max-w-md">
                  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">ABOUT</h1>
                 
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold my-4">Key Features</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-8">
                <li>EJS template engine integration for dynamic data rendering</li>
                <li>Random quote feature using the 'Quotable' API</li>
                <li>Partial views for common HTML elements like the navbar</li>
                <li>Data sets rendered using EJS with table display for toys data</li>
                <li>Functionality for creating, updating, and deleting Lego sets</li>
                <li>User account management with MongoDB Atlas for authentication and sessions</li>
                <li>Login history functionality to track user logins</li>
                <li>Utilization of Tailwind CSS with DaisyUI plugin for responsive UI design</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
